<ol class="results"></ol> 
</div>

The *for loop*

<div class="code-block console-wrap">
<div class="code-block code">
<code class="PHP">
counter = 0
for  counter = 1, 10 do
   print(counter)
end
</code>
</div>
<div  id ="msg1" class="msg">
</div>
<div class="console"></div>
